{"tid":1458513,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手屌醒教畜","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:00:18.000Z","uid":86347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4888d1b4cafb5374038bb4d958b9e2248cd88dc","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100000631803304/posts/2612858972078471?s=532445858&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100000631803304%2Fposts%2F2612858972078471%3Fs%3D532445858%26sfns%3Dmo&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=275caff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100000631803304/posts/2612858972078471?s=532445858&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n佢其他post都極on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教過poly<br />\n而加係崑山科技大學做教授<br />\n似係真心覺得自己無錯<br />\n唔可以再俾呢d人教下一代<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ma.ksu.edu.tw/T094000165.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ma.ksu.edu.tw%2FT094000165.html&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=29a5abb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ma.ksu.edu.tw/T094000165.html</a><br />\n史文鴻 教授\t<br />\n\t專長<br />\n\t批判社會理論<br />\n分析哲學<br />\n電影理論<br />\n文化研究。<br />\n\t學歷<br />\n\t德國自由大學─哲學博士<br />\n\t學術資格<br />\n\t哲學博士(Ph.D)德國自由大學 1986年<br />\n哲學碩士(M.Ph.)香港中文文學研究院 1979年<br />\n文學學士(B.A) 1977年<br />\n\t研究及興趣範圍<br />\n\t批判社會理論<br />\n分析哲學<br />\n電影理論<br />\n文化研究<br />\n\t工作經驗<br />\n\t◆香港自由黨行政總幹事(CEO) 2004年2月至2005年9月。<br />\n◆首席講師(相當於大學教授) 2000年8月至2004年1月 (香港理工大學通識教育中心)。<br />\n◆高級講師(相當於大學副教授) 1998年8月至2000年7月 (香港理工大學通識教育中心)。<br />\n◆副教授(Associate Professor) 1997年8月至1998年7月 (香港嶺南學院通識教育部)。<br />\n◆大學講師(University Lecturer) (相當於大學助理到副教授) 1991年8月至(香港嶺南學院通識教育部) 1997年7月。<br />\n◆講師(相當於大學助理教授) 1989年8月至1991年7月 (香港理工學院太右設計學院)。<br />\n◆講師(相當於大學助理教授) 1987年8月至1989年7月 (香港 會學院傳理系)。<br />\n\t社會公職服務<br />\n\t香港政府-香港電台及電視部(RTHK)顧問 (1993至今)<br />\n香港政府-香港最高法院委任&quot;淫褻及不雅物品&quot;審裁員(1996至今)<br />\n香港政府康文署電影節目顧問(1998至今)<br />\n\tE-mail:<br />\n\tszemh@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"37af0375ccff88dec4c8ead3b9561ba1e2c162e2","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"有無手足知台灣點投訴"},{"pid":"f7ac39cb392e1f8bc65de61ee268846b1a118a6c","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7831db1b0b6f532b5dfcedf38a188a6daa278a30","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:21:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a063dae6c1669676723e00f1870956e090057742","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92180ac1db41b582dd1d5dc6d4a987aef96a7ff5","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a8f1b33d2383dad2351d9468b68a372310c4872","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5778a57ce363d81baf0092ef5ecd8b99f89a923b","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76a2d7a9019a73f2bdc201bf490cfdc1868f1679","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e82d723149e1ced03869013c449a64b12f6360e","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:27:12.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"ce42e1c40b5801c723389bd2ff5ad75cbe7ba569","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:27:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"34600071a886a82e69f3f359470ec62f8ce64939","tid":1458513,"uid":86347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:29:09